== Bangogo ==

Bisina ya bangogo ya Kituba kele [[kikongo]], [[lingala]], [[kiyaka]], [[kiyansi]], [[kiswahili]], [[kifalanse]] ye [[kimputulukesi]].

=== Bangogo ya kifalanse ===

*falangi (''franc'')
*kaminio (''camion'')
*kaye (''cahier'')
*leta (''l'état'')
*sose (''sauce'')
*tono (''tonneau'')
*watu (''ouate'')

=== Bangogo ya kimputulukesi ===

*kilapi (''lápis'')
*kumbi (''comboio'')
*mapa (''mapa'')
*misa (''missa'')
